OL,3,CHistoric religious site on fire and
OL,4,Cfive dead as Russia strikes Ukraine
OL,6,FA large-scale Russian attack on
OL,7,FUkraine killed five rescuers in
OL,8,FKharkiv and wounded at least 20 people
OL,9,Fin the capital Kyiv on Monday, as
OL,10,Fstrikes set apartment buildings ablaze
OL,11,Fand sparked a fire at one of the
OL,12,Fcountry's most significant religious
OL,13,Flandmarks.
OL,15,FThe rescuers were killed in Kharkiv by
OL,16,Fa second Russian strike as they fought
OL,17,Fa blaze caused by an earlier attack,
OL,18,FInterior Minister Ihor Klymenko said.
OL,19,FAt least five other emergency workers
OL,20,Fwere wounded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
