OL,3,CHistoric religious site on fire and
OL,4,Cfive dead as Russia strikes Ukraine
OL,6,FA series of powerful explosions echoed
OL,7,Facross Kyiv, with a wave of ballistic
OL,8,Fmissiles followed by Shahed drones as
OL,9,Fmany people sought shelter underground
OL,10,Fand officials urged residents to take
OL,11,Fcover.
OL,13,F"Kyiv is under the main strike. There
OL,14,Fis significant destruction of civilian
OL,15,Finfrastructure," Klymenko said.
OL,17,FTwenty people, including a child,
OL,18,Fsought medical help in the capital,
OL,19,Fsaid Tymur Tkachenko, head of the Kyiv
OL,20,FCity Military Administration.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@PO]
