OL,3,CHistoric religious site on fire and
OL,4,Cfive dead as Russia strikes Ukraine
OL,6,FFive strikes hit civilian sites in the
OL,7,Fcity's Shevchenkivskyi district in
OL,8,Fless than 30 minutes, he said,
OL,9,Fincluding a 25-story apartment
OL,10,Fbuilding, while a market and a grocery
OL,11,Fstore caught fire. In the Obolonskyi
OL,12,Fdistrict, a nine-story residential
OL,13,Fbuilding took a direct hit.
OL,15,FTkachenko accused Russia of striking
OL,16,Fapartment blocks on purpose.
OL,18,F"This is their deliberate decision,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@dO]
