OL,3,CHistoric religious site on fire and
OL,4,Cfive dead as Russia strikes Ukraine
OL,6,FDamage at the Kyiv-Pechersk Lavra, a
OL,7,Fmonastic complex, was substantial and
OL,8,Fa serious fire had broken out, said
OL,9,FTkachenko, who accused Russia of
OL,10,Fdeliberately striking "the heart of
OL,11,Fone of the largest Christian shrines."
OL,13,FThe roof of the Dormition Cathedral
OL,14,Fcaught fire during the overnight
OL,15,Fattack, said Metropolitan Epiphanius,
OL,16,Fhead of the Orthodox Church of
OL,17,FUkraine. He condemned the strike as
OL,18,Fanother Russian crime "against
OL,19,Fhumanity, against history, against
OL,20,FChristianity" and appealed for prayers
OL,21,Fto save the site.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@fO]zD@WOU|D@MO]
