OL,3,CHistoric religious site on fire and
OL,4,Cfive dead as Russia strikes Ukraine
OL,6,FThe Kyiv-Pechersk Lavra, also known as
OL,7,Fthe Monastery of the Caves, is a
OL,8,Fsprawling complex of monasteries and
OL,9,Fchurches, including some underground,
OL,10,Fbuilt from the 11th to the 19th
OL,11,Fcentury. Some of the churches at the
OL,12,FUNESCO-listed World Heritage site are
OL,13,Fconnected by a labyrinthine complex of
OL,14,Fcaves spanning more than 600 meters
OL,15,F(2,000 feet).
OL,17,FThe cathedral, churches and other
OL,18,Fbuildings overlook the right bank of
OL,19,Fthe Dnipro River and have been a
OL,20,Fpilgrimage site for centuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
